Above Alliance Island, the impressive form of Vampiza flys. Stright 
over the Iron fist and the old base of the alliance.  Meanwhile, 
Inside the Oblivion of Pherical hologram of the Earth shows Darkfate 
approaching the area of the Infecticon ship. Not one to waste time 
Frostbite taps a green button. A moment the later the ocean beaneath 
Darkfate seemingly egins to bulge before it parts off to the side to 
show a bright circular energy field hoding the sea from falling in on 
the ship. On another portion of the ship, two small portions open up 
before two odd looking ships seemingly flying like a vertical like 
exit and fire out into the ocean. Each then flys off towards the 
surface before they break through and the bottom folds out into 
wings. Each one passenger ship then speeds off towards the location 
of the IGL transmission.
